EarnedConcreteUnitTest
├── When the caller is not the token owner
│   └── It should revert with {NA}
└── When the caller is the token owner
    ├── When there are no claimable rewards
    │   └── It should return zero
    └── When there are claimable rewards
        ├── When penalty rate is zero
        │   └── It should return full rewards
        └── When penalty rate is greater than zero
            ├── When called within min stake time
            │   └── It should return rewards minus penalty
            └── When called after min stake time
                └── It should return full rewards
